- [ Scoffs ] I'm not scared, okay?
- [Hissing Sound]

436
00:28:44,159 --> 00:28:46,719
[ Whimpers ]

437
00:28:46,799 --> 00:28:50,479
I just don't know why
we have to be here, that's all.

438
00:28:50,559 --> 00:28:53,359
If Kovu is so special,
why does he need us?

439
00:28:53,439 --> 00:28:56,079
- [Hissing]
- I never even had a chance!

440
00:28:56,159 --> 00:28:59,279
[ Screaming, Whimpering ]

441
00:29:01,919 --> 00:29:04,879
That's it!
Well, come on.

442
00:29:05,039 --> 00:29:07,679
Kiara has started her hunt.
We have to move quickly.

443
00:29:07,759 --> 00:29:10,399
[ Whimpering ]

444
00:29:10,479 --> 00:29:13,439
Ow, fire!

445
00:29:13,519 --> 00:29:15,839
[ Laughs Hysterically ]

446
00:29:20,639 --> 00:29:22,559
Ah!

447
00:29:24,959 --> 00:29:27,119
Hut! Hut!

448
00:29:27,199 --> 00:29:30,079
[ Grass Rustling ]

449
00:29:44,239 --> 00:29:46,559
Tango Charlie Alpha.
What's your position?

450
00:29:46,639 --> 00:29:52,159
Uh... upright? Head turned
slightly to the left, tail erect.

451
00:29:52,239 --> 00:29:54,959
Why do I bother?

452
00:29:56,639 --> 00:29:58,719
Aha!

453
00:30:00,479 --> 00:30:04,239
- Ooh.
- [ Stone Rattles ]

454
00:30:07,919 --> 00:30:09,839
[ Gasps ]

455
00:30:18,319 --> 00:30:20,959
[ Both Screaming ]

456
00:30:21,119 --> 00:30:24,399
[ Timon ] This must be where
the deer and the antelope play.

457
00:30:24,479 --> 00:30:27,199
- [ Screaming ]
- [ Panting ]

458
00:30:27,279 --> 00:30:30,799
- [ Laughing Uneasily ]
- Timon, what are you doing here?

459
00:30:30,879 --> 00:30:34,079
Uh, shopping!
We thought a nice pelt for the den,

460
00:30:34,159 --> 00:30:36,159
some throw pillows,
a little potpourri...

461
00:30:36,239 --> 00:30:40,479
My father sent you. After he promised
to let me do this on my own, he lied.

462
00:30:40,559 --> 00:30:43,359
No. He just doesn't
want you to get hurt.

463
00:30:43,519 --> 00:30:47,039
I should have known
he'd never give me a real chance.

464
00:30:47,119 --> 00:30:51,039
I'll do this on my own!
Away from the pride lands.

465
00:30:51,119 --> 00:30:53,679
Hey! Wait!
Come back! Ah!

466
00:30:53,759 --> 00:30:56,959
- [ Pumbaa ] Look behind you!
- [ Timon ] Kiara! Come back!

467
00:30:57,039 --> 00:30:59,599
Oh-ho! She's gone again.

468
00:30:59,679 --> 00:31:03,279
Somebody's gotta get
a beeper for this kid.

469
00:31:06,319 --> 00:31:08,479
[ Panting ]

470
00:31:13,199 --> 00:31:15,919
[ Nuka ]
Let's light fires!

471
00:31:15,999 --> 00:31:18,399
[ Chuckling ]

472
00:31:18,479 --> 00:31:21,519
[ Yelling, Laughing ]

473
00:31:21,679 --> 00:31:26,159
<i><font color=cyan>¶ Roasty-toasty princess
roasty-toasty princess ¶</i>

474
00:31:26,239 --> 00:31:29,519
Hey, is it hot in here,
or is that just me?

475
00:31:29,599 --> 00:31:32,559
Fire!
[ Screaming ]

476
00:31:32,639 --> 00:31:35,839
- [ Laughing ]
- Come on.

477
00:31:44,639 --> 00:31:47,679
Wha...

478
00:31:53,839 --> 00:31:55,759
[ Gasps ]

479
00:32:03,919 --> 00:32:07,599
The plan is in motion. Go!

480
00:32:13,359 --> 00:32:16,959
Don't worry, Simba.
She'll be fine!

481
00:32:17,039 --> 00:32:19,039
What could happen?

482
00:32:19,119 --> 00:32:22,479
[ Gasps ]
No! No! Kiara!

483
00:32:22,559 --> 00:32:26,479
- [ Gasps ]
- Zazu! Fly ahead! Find her!

484
00:32:26,559 --> 00:32:29,119
- [ Growling ]
- [ Frightened Neighing ]

485
00:32:31,039 --> 00:32:34,399
[ Panting ]
Oh!

486
00:32:34,479 --> 00:32:36,399
[ Screams ]

487
00:32:37,599 --> 00:32:39,599
[ Coughing ]

488
00:32:45,599 --> 00:32:47,919
No!

489
00:32:50,959 --> 00:32:53,599
[ Panting, Grunting ]

490
00:32:55,839 --> 00:32:58,479
[ Grunting, Sighing ]

491
00:33:03,999 --> 00:33:07,439
- [ Deep Growling ]
- [ Moaning ]

492
00:33:10,719 --> 00:33:12,639
[ Growling ]

493
00:33:12,719 --> 00:33:14,639
[ Sighing ]

494
00:33:22,559 --> 00:33:24,479
[ Snarling ]

495
00:33:45,919 --> 00:33:48,159
[ Kovu Grunting ]

496
00:33:50,159 --> 00:33:52,159
[ Gasps ]

497
00:33:57,919 --> 00:33:59,679
[ Gasps ]

498
00:34:01,119 --> 00:34:03,839
I must tell Simba!

499
00:34:09,039 --> 00:34:11,599
[ Coughing, Gasping ]

500
00:34:13,759 --> 00:34:18,639
- Where am I ?
- You're safe. In the pride lands.

501
00:34:18,679 --> 00:34:21,759
The pride lands? No!

502
00:34:21,839 --> 00:34:24,319
Why'd you bring me here?
Who do you think you are?

503
00:34:24,439 --> 00:34:27,759
[ Gasps ] I think I'm the one
that just saved your life.

504
00:34:27,839 --> 00:34:30,319
Look, I had everything
under control.

505
00:34:30,399 --> 00:34:33,359
- Not from where I'm standing.
- Then move downwind.

506
00:34:33,519 --> 00:34:35,759
[ Growls ]

507
00:34:37,359 --> 00:34:40,079
[ Grunts, Sighs, Growls ]

508
00:34:43,759 --> 00:34:45,839
What are you doing?

509
00:34:46,919 --> 00:34:49,359
Kovu?

510
00:34:49,439 --> 00:34:52,679
Kiara!
[Snarling]

511
00:34:52,719 --> 00:34:54,919
Kiara, you're all right.

512
00:34:55,039 --> 00:34:56,919
Father, how could you
break your promise?

513
00:34:57,039 --> 00:34:59,359
It's a good thing I did.
I almost lost you.

514
00:34:59,439 --> 00:35:01,359
No more hunts for you.
Not ever.

515
00:35:01,439 --> 00:35:04,159
But I was doing just fine!
Even before Kovu...

516
00:35:04,239 --> 00:35:07,519
- Kovu?
- [Both Snarling]

517
00:35:07,599 --> 00:35:09,839
- Simba!
- [ Growling ]

518
00:35:09,919 --> 00:35:11,919
Hey! You!

519
00:35:11,999 --> 00:35:15,599
How dare you save the king's daughter?

520
00:35:15,679 --> 00:35:18,439
You saved her? Why?

521
00:35:18,559 --> 00:35:21,919
- I humbly ask to join your pride.
- No!

522
00:35:22,079 --> 00:35:24,399
You were banished
with the other outsiders.

523
00:35:24,439 --> 00:35:27,519
I have left the outsiders.
I am a rogue.

524
00:35:27,599 --> 00:35:31,279
Judge me now for who l am.
[Sighing]

525
00:35:31,359 --> 00:35:35,919
Or am I to be blamed
for a crime I didn't commit?

526
00:35:35,999 --> 00:35:38,879
[ Growling ]

527
00:35:38,919 --> 00:35:41,759
Simba, you owe him
your daughter's life.

528
00:35:43,439 --> 00:35:46,159
Hmm, yes, sire.
Clearly we are in his debt.

529
00:35:46,239 --> 00:35:49,679
And royal protocol demands
that all debts be paid.

530
00:35:49,759 --> 00:35:52,559
Though in this case,
you might want to make an exception.

531
00:35:52,679 --> 00:35:54,919
Hmm.

532
00:35:57,679 --> 00:36:00,679
My father's law will prevail.

533
00:36:00,799 --> 00:36:03,599
For now, I reserve judgment.

534
00:36:03,679 --> 00:36:05,759
We'll see who you really are.

535
00:36:05,839 --> 00:36:07,919
Hmm.

536
00:36:09,159 --> 00:36:11,439
Hmph! Riffraff.

537
00:36:16,239 --> 00:36:18,159
[ Growling ]

538
00:36:29,039 --> 00:36:31,039
[ Gasps ]

539
00:36:32,679 --> 00:36:34,879
[ Growls ]

540
00:36:59,439 --> 00:37:03,519
Hey, uh, thanks for saving me today.

541
00:37:03,679 --> 00:37:07,119
[ Laughs ] What kind of hunter
are you, anyway... Princess?

542
00:37:07,159 --> 00:37:09,359
You almost got yourself killed out there.

543
00:37:09,519 --> 00:37:13,359
- What?
- You wouldn't last three days on your own.

544
00:37:13,359 --> 00:37:16,719
Oh, and I suppose you could teach me?

545
00:37:16,799 --> 00:37:18,919
[ Laughs ]
Oh. Yeah.

546
00:37:18,959 --> 00:37:21,839
- [Simba] Kiara!
- Coming.

547
00:37:23,519 --> 00:37:26,639
All right! Impress me.

548
00:37:26,679 --> 00:37:29,159
We start at dawn.

549
00:37:30,879 --> 00:37:34,919
[ Chuckling ]
I look forward to it.

550
00:37:37,679 --> 00:37:41,839
[ Sputtering ]
Did you see that?

551
00:37:41,919 --> 00:37:45,119
- He let her go! lf that were me, l...
- Hush.

552
00:37:45,159 --> 00:37:47,119
The fire rescue worked perfectly,

553
00:37:47,159 --> 00:37:49,119
and Simba fell for it.

554
00:37:49,159 --> 00:37:52,399
Now, the closer Kovu
gets to the daughter,

555
00:37:52,479 --> 00:37:55,599
the closer he gets to Simba!

556
00:37:57,359 --> 00:38:00,799
And once he has Simba alone...
[ Snarls ]

557
00:38:07,919 --> 00:38:09,919
[ Panting, Grunting ]

558
00:38:11,279 --> 00:38:14,799
[Male Voice, Echoing]
Simba! Simba!

559
00:38:14,919 --> 00:38:18,639
- Help me!
- Father!

560
00:38:18,719 --> 00:38:23,039
[Evil Laughing, Echoing]

561
00:38:23,159 --> 00:38:26,159
No! Dad!

562
00:38:26,239 --> 00:38:28,919
Just a little farther.

563
00:38:30,959 --> 00:38:32,919
- [Scar] Gotcha!
- [ Screams ]

564
00:38:32,959 --> 00:38:37,839
- Trust me.
- Simba!

565
00:38:37,919 --> 00:38:40,439
No!

566
00:38:40,439 --> 00:38:44,319
- Scar.
- [ Laughing ]

567
00:38:46,319 --> 00:38:48,239
- Kovu?
- Hyah!

568
00:38:48,319 --> 00:38:52,919
No!

569
00:38:52,959 --> 00:38:56,479
[ Panting, Gasping ]

570
00:39:31,519 --> 00:39:36,439
[ Growling ]

571
00:39:37,999 --> 00:39:40,159
Good morning.
[ Laughing ]

572
00:39:40,319 --> 00:39:44,399
I'm ready for my first lesson.
Surprised ya, huh?

573
00:39:45,839 --> 00:39:49,199
Hey, come on.
[ Laughing ] Let's go.

574
00:39:52,559 --> 00:39:54,479
[ Growling ]

575
00:39:58,919 --> 00:40:02,919
- [Grass Rustling]
- [Panting] Ow.

576
00:40:06,399 --> 00:40:08,319
Ow! Ow.

577
00:40:08,439 --> 00:40:11,039
[ Sighing ]

578
00:40:11,159 --> 00:40:13,999
Three, two, one.

579
00:40:14,079 --> 00:40:17,039
Gotcha!

580
00:40:17,039 --> 00:40:19,679
You could hear me, huh?

581
00:40:19,759 --> 00:40:21,679
Only a lot.

582
00:40:23,359 --> 00:40:25,279
You're still breathing too hard.

583
00:40:25,359 --> 00:40:28,719
Relax. Feel the earth under your paws,

584
00:40:28,879 --> 00:40:31,359
so it doesn't shift and make noise.

585
00:40:31,439 --> 00:40:33,359
- [ Sighs ]
- [ Birds Calling ]

586
00:40:35,199 --> 00:40:39,839
Shh! Watch the master and learn.

587
00:40:43,999 --> 00:40:46,879
- [ Roaring ]
- [ Screaming ]

588
00:40:46,919 --> 00:40:48,879
Don't eat me, please.

589
00:40:48,919 --> 00:40:52,239
I-l-l never really met your tyrant...
I mean, uh, Scar. Scar.

590
00:40:52,399 --> 00:40:54,239
Oh, heck of a guy.
A little moody, but...

591
00:40:54,399 --> 00:40:57,599
Timon, what are you doing here?

592
00:40:57,679 --> 00:41:00,079
Kiara! Thank goodness!

593
00:41:00,079 --> 00:41:03,039
Oh! Hey, for once,
we're not followin' ya.

594
00:41:03,119 --> 00:41:06,439
This just happens to be
the best smorgasbord in the pride lands.

595
00:41:06,559 --> 00:41:09,119
Bugs everywhere!

596
00:41:09,199 --> 00:41:12,159
But, you don't call
for a reservation, and... Yeesh!

597
00:41:12,239 --> 00:41:15,039
Get outta here, ya scavengers.
Go on! Shoo!

598
00:41:15,159 --> 00:41:17,279
- Shoo! Ow!
- [ Swallowing ]

599
00:41:17,439 --> 00:41:20,919
[ Crying ]
Oh-ho-ho. Oh!

600
00:41:20,959 --> 00:41:23,679
[ Screaming Wildly ]

601
00:41:23,759 --> 00:41:26,919
[ Laughing, Screaming Wildly ]

602
00:41:26,959 --> 00:41:31,759
- [ Laughing ]
- Oh, Timon! l'm gettin' tired.

603
00:41:31,839 --> 00:41:34,439
I gotta lose some pounds.

604
00:41:34,559 --> 00:41:36,679
Shoo! Go on!
Shoo! Shoo!

605
00:41:36,719 --> 00:41:39,359
- [ Laughing ]
- Hey, maybe he could help.

606
00:41:39,439 --> 00:41:41,359
- Do you think?
- Shoo!

607
00:41:41,439 --> 00:41:44,959
Oh, yeah, there's an idea.
Right. Let the vicious outsider...

608
00:41:45,119 --> 00:41:47,999
Hey! Wait!
I have an idea.

609
00:41:49,279 --> 00:41:51,599
- What if he helps?
- What?

610
00:41:51,679 --> 00:41:54,919
You want to lend a voice? Hah?

611
00:41:54,959 --> 00:41:58,239
Grr. Gr...
Roar! Work with me!

612
00:41:58,319 --> 00:42:01,439
- Uh, huh?
- Like this. [ Roaring ]

613
00:42:01,519 --> 00:42:03,599
- [ Roaring Continues ]
- [ Birds Chirping ]

614
00:42:03,759 --> 00:42:06,679
Whoo-hoo! Come on.
Do it again. Do it again.

615
00:42:06,799 --> 00:42:10,239
- [ Louder Roaring ]
- [ Timon ] Yee-ha! [ Blows Raspberry ]

616
00:42:10,239 --> 00:42:13,679
Why are we doing this?
What's the point of this training?

617
00:42:13,759 --> 00:42:16,439
[ Laughing ]
Training? This is just for fun!

618
00:42:18,919 --> 00:42:20,879
- Fun?
- [ Laughing ]

619
00:42:20,919 --> 00:42:23,279
Yeesh, kid.
Ya gotta get out more often.

620
00:42:23,359 --> 00:42:25,679
Fun! Yee-ha!

621
00:42:25,759 --> 00:42:28,239
[ Laughing ]

622
00:42:28,319 --> 00:42:30,719
Woo-hoo! Yee-ha!

623
00:42:30,799 --> 00:42:32,719
- Yee-ha!
- [ Laughing ]

624
00:42:32,799 --> 00:42:34,559
- Yee-ha!
- [ Birds Twittering ]

625
00:42:36,559 --> 00:42:39,159
[ Timon ]
Whoa-oh-oh! [ Laughs ]

626
00:42:39,199 --> 00:42:41,599
- Yee-ha!
- [Kiara] Yee-ha!

627
00:42:41,759 --> 00:42:44,079
[ All Laughing ]

628
00:42:44,159 --> 00:42:47,119
[ Screaming ]

629
00:42:47,159 --> 00:42:49,839
- Uh-oh.
- [ Blowing Raspberry ]

630
00:42:49,919 --> 00:42:52,679
- [ Bellowing ]
- Wow!

631
00:42:52,719 --> 00:42:54,679
[ All ]
Yee-ha!

632
00:42:59,119 --> 00:43:00,959
- Whoa!
- Whoa!

633
00:43:01,119 --> 00:43:02,959
[ Timon ]
Hey, rhino!

634
00:43:06,159 --> 00:43:10,319
[ Laughing ]

635
00:43:10,439 --> 00:43:13,839
- What a blast!
- Oh. Sorry.

636
00:43:13,919 --> 00:43:16,399
- [ Kovu, Kiara Laughing ]
- Aha! You're okay, kid.

637
00:43:16,439 --> 00:43:18,439
- Hey!
- You're okay.

638
00:43:18,479 --> 00:43:21,599
- Kid.
- Excuse me. Pardon me. Pardon me.

639
00:43:21,679 --> 00:43:24,799
- [ Groaning ]
- That's it. That's it. That's it. Ooh...

640
00:43:24,879 --> 00:43:28,679
- A-Ahem. [ Laughing ]
- [ Laughing ]

641
00:43:28,679 --> 00:43:34,159
- Um... S-Sorry. Uh...
- [ Stammering ]

642
00:43:34,159 --> 00:43:37,519
- [ Timon ] Hey, are you two coming or what?
- [ Kiara Giggling ]

643
00:43:42,799 --> 00:43:45,599
[Kovu]Did you see that?
Did you see that? Watch.

644
00:43:45,679 --> 00:43:49,279
- Oh, wow. Look at that. It's really pretty.
- What? Oh, yeah.

645
00:43:49,359 --> 00:43:52,719
You're right.
Oh, look!

646
00:43:52,799 --> 00:43:56,399
There's one that looks like
a baby rabbit. See the fluffy tail?

647
00:43:56,479 --> 00:43:59,039
Yeah. Hey!

648
00:43:59,119 --> 00:44:02,479
There's one that looks like two lions
killing each other for a scrap of meat.

649
00:44:02,559 --> 00:44:05,279
[Laughs]
Hey, I've never done this before.

650
00:44:05,359 --> 00:44:10,719
Really? My father and I
used to do this all the time.

651
00:44:10,879 --> 00:44:15,839
He says all the great kings
of the past are up there. [ Chuckles ]

652
00:44:15,919 --> 00:44:18,079
[ Whispering ]
Do ya think Scar's up there?

653
00:44:25,599 --> 00:44:29,359
He wasn't my father,
but he was still... part of me.

654
00:44:31,759 --> 00:44:34,559
My father said there was a...

655
00:44:34,719 --> 00:44:39,119
a darkness in Scar
that he couldn't escape.

656
00:44:39,199 --> 00:44:44,159
Maybe there's a darkness in me too.

657
00:44:44,239 --> 00:44:46,879
[ Purring ]

658
00:44:53,279 --> 00:44:58,479
Father, I am lost.
Kovu is one of them.

659
00:44:58,559 --> 00:45:00,879
Scar's heir.

660
00:45:00,959 --> 00:45:03,599
- How can I accept him?
- Simba?

661
00:45:07,039 --> 00:45:10,079
I was seeking counsel
from the great kings.

662
00:45:10,239 --> 00:45:12,639
- Did they help?
- [ Sighs ]

663
00:45:12,719 --> 00:45:15,599
[ Simba ]
Silent as stars. My father would never...

664
00:45:15,759 --> 00:45:17,599
Oh, my Simba.

665
00:45:17,759 --> 00:45:21,039
You want so much
to walk the path expected of you.

666
00:45:21,119 --> 00:45:24,879
- Perhaps Kovu does not.
- What? How do you know...

667
00:45:24,959 --> 00:45:30,079
[ Laughing ] I can see them down there
Just as easily as you can.

668
00:45:30,159 --> 00:45:32,399
Get to know him and see.

669
00:45:44,639 --> 00:45:47,119
- [ Clears Throat ]
- What's wrong?

670
00:45:47,279 --> 00:45:49,759
Nothing.

671
00:45:49,839 --> 00:45:53,679
- Kovu...
- It's just that my whole life
I've been trained to...

672
00:45:53,759 --> 00:45:55,679
[ Sighs ]
Nothing.

673
00:45:55,759 --> 00:45:58,639
- I gotta go.
- Kovu, wait.

674
00:46:05,199 --> 00:46:07,279
[ Rafiki ]
And where are you going?

675
00:46:07,359 --> 00:46:09,839
N-Nowhere.

676
00:46:09,999 --> 00:46:12,639
Ha! That's what you think!
[ Laughs ]

677
00:46:14,079 --> 00:46:17,439
- Who was that?
- Uh, friend of the family.

678
